Import Water Quality data from rds files

ss_import_data.Rd

Import Water Quality data from rds files

Usage

ss_import_data(input_path = NULL, county = "all")

Arguments

input_path

Path to the *.rds files to be assembled. Default is the assembled_data folder on the CMAR R drive (user must be connected to the Perennia VPN).

county

Vector of character string(s) indicating which county or counties for which to import data. For efficiency, the filter is applied to the file path, so the county name MUST be part of the file path. Defaults to all counties.
